            <thetext>Just tested an application with the iOS 8 beta Safari. Something is broken with the label size. It starts to paint ellipsis even if the text normally fits in the available space.

Reproduce: Open the Playground i.E. on an iPad with iOS 8 and add four more characters to the preset button text

You can see the effect in the demo browser, too.

Sure, iOS 8 is in beta state, but... ;-)</thetext>
